    "slot_count": 3,
    "source_text": "於2020年12月31日，我們的主要營運公司友邦保險有限公司（AIA Co.）的償付能力充足率仍然非常強勁，為\n489%。於2020年12月31日，在新的集團監管框架下，集團當地資本總和法覆蓋率為374%。日後，我們將披露集\n團當地資本總和法覆蓋率，作為衡量本集團監管償付能力的主要指標。",
    "current_translation": "As at 31 December 2020, the solvency ratio of our principal operating company, AIA Company Limited (AIA Co.), remained very strong at 489%. As at 31 December 2020, under the new group supervisory framework, the Group LCSM cover ratio was 374%. Going forward, we will disclose the Group LCSM cover ratio as the primary measure of the Group's regulatory solvency."
